Package: SLOcatoR
Title: Annotate Single-Cells from Secondary Lymphoid Organs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ramon", "Massoni-Badosa", email="ramon.massoni@cnag.crg.eu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Paula", "Soler-Vila", email="PSOLER@clinic.cat", role = "aut"))      
Description: This package is aimed at annotating and visualizing single-cell
    gene expression or chromatin accessibility profiles from secondary lymphoid 
    organs (SLO) using the tonsil atlas as reference.
